.br
.RS
.PP
Calls \fIwxTranslations::AddCatalog(const wxString&, wxLanguage)\fR (not implemented in wx).


.RE
.B
\fBaddCatalog(This, Domain, MsgIdLanguage, MsgIdCharset) -> boolean()\fR
\fB                    when\fR
\fB                        This :: wxLocale(),\fR
\fB                        Domain :: unicode:chardata(),\fR
